      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">The Raw Numbers</h2>
      <p>Let's start with the baseline mathematics. A standard Scrabble bag contains 100 tiles with a specific distribution of letters. When you draw 7 tiles at random, the probability of forming a valid word depends on which letters you get.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
