          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">50</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Bonus points</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>A completely random draw of 7 tiles from a full bag has roughly a 5-12% chance of containing letters that form at least one valid 7-letter word. That percentage increases significantly when you manage your rack toward favourable combinations.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">How Rack Composition Affects Probability</h2>
      <p>Not all racks are created equal. The vowel-to-consonant ratio and the specific letters you hold dramatically shift your bingo odds.</p>

