      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">The Blank Tile Effect</h2>
      <p>Blank tiles are probability multipliers. A blank can represent any letter, which exponentially increases the number of valid 7-letter words your rack can form.</p>

