          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">2</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Blanks in the bag</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Holding one blank alongside a bingo stem like SATINE gives you a near-certain bingo. The blank fills whatever gap exists, making almost any 7th tile workable. This is why expert players never waste blanks on short words.</p>

